cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper focuses on developing a novel open-set instance segmentation algorithm for point clouds in the context of autonomous driving. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by robotics (cs.RO) as the paper deals with autonomous driving. The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques to some extent, which could place it in the computational linguistics (cs.CL) category.
